title: Module 10: Using Asset Transfer SDK: Part 1
description: Welcome to Module 10 of the Router Nitro Cookbook. This Module focuses on Utilizing the Asset Transfer SDK of Router Protocol. This SDK, available as an npm Package, Streamlines Asset Swapping between Blockchains. By installing the Package and importing required Libraries, you can Seamlessly Transfer Assets across Different Blockchains.
